name: Culmullin
info: Penultimate race week and in a change to the planned circuit, we'll do Culmullin circuit which we haven't done this year yet
Race will be 2 laps and will have the usual finish on the Dunshaughlin road (~43km)
Plan is for 4 races depending on numbers
Sign-on in usual place on R125. Sign on closes at 6.50pm, races start at 7pm sharp
